{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/mbiesiad/awesome-translations/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e902015f-2906-5cee-a97d-d134482078dc","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-translations-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-translations-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome translations awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Translations <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge-flat.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The transfer of the meaning of a text from one language to another.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>This list contains tools, books, articles, blogs, courses and everything related to translations (<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Translation\">t9n</a> - translation, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Language_localisation\">l10n</a> - localization, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Language_localisation#Globalisation_versus_localisation\">g11n</a> - globalization, <a href=\"https://www.definify.com/word/multilingualization#:~:text=Noun,into%2C%20or%20for%20multiple%20languages\">m17n</a> - multilingualization, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Language_localisation#Globalisation_versus_localisation\">i18n</a> - internationalization, synonymous with globalization).</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anch